text: Anostostoma is the type genus of the family Anostostomatidae and consists of five species of insect, endemic to Australia.Genus Anostostoma == Included species == * Anostostoma australasiae Gray, 1837 * Anostostoma erinaceum (Burmeister, 1838) * Anostostoma femorale Walker, 1869 * Anostostoma opacum Brunner von Wattenwyl, 1888 * Anostostoma spinosum Karny, 1930 == Formerly included == * Stenopelmatus toltecus (Saussure, 1861)Stenopelmatus toltecus == References == Category:Weta Category:Ensifera genera Category:Stenopelmatoidea
title: Anostostoma
